He must kneel on one knee,

13
00:02:02,920 --> 00:02:03,960
hand the ring

14
00:02:03,960 --> 00:02:05,790
and say loads of cheesy lines.

15
00:02:05,790 --> 00:02:07,000
The crowd would cheer for them

16
00:02:07,000 --> 00:02:08,110
and say,

17
00:02:08,110 --> 00:02:09,740
"Marry him, marry him!"

18
00:02:11,470 --> 00:02:12,710
What does it have to do with them?

19
00:02:12,710 --> 00:02:13,990
It's none of their businesses.

20
00:02:14,830 --> 00:02:16,200
Marriage is supposed to be

21
00:02:16,200 --> 00:02:16,840
an important decision

22
00:02:16,870 --> 00:02:18,480
made by two people

23
00:02:18,520 --> 00:02:20,070
after thinking rationally.

24
00:02:20,200 --> 00:02:21,040
When did it

25
00:02:21,040 --> 00:02:21,880
become a fancy show?

26
00:02:22,750 --> 00:02:24,160
Proposing in public

27
00:02:24,200 --> 00:02:25,550
is using the pressure from the crowd

28
00:02:25,550 --> 00:02:27,430
to force the other one to say yes.

29
00:02:27,430 --> 00:02:29,000
