30
00:02:29,240 --> 00:02:30,040
It's just for show.

31
00:02:41,870 --> 00:02:43,630
Are these people enough?

32
00:02:44,560 --> 00:02:46,400
Who else can I invite?

33
00:02:48,270 --> 00:02:49,670
Give it another thought.

34
00:02:50,880 --> 00:02:52,430
Both parties are willing.

35
00:02:53,840 --> 00:02:54,880
Think about it,

36
00:02:55,150 --> 00:02:56,280
the grass,

37
00:02:56,280 --> 00:02:57,710
the balloons,

38
00:02:57,710 --> 00:02:58,840
the curtains.

39
00:02:59,150 --> 00:03:00,320
And...

40
00:03:01,520 --> 00:03:02,640
And…

41
00:03:03,510 --> 00:03:04,350
Candles.

42
00:03:06,710 --> 00:03:07,390
Candles.

43
00:03:07,550 --> 00:03:09,230
In a dark room,

44
00:03:09,230 --> 00:03:10,600
candles are arranged

45
00:03:10,640 --> 00:03:11,990
in the shape of a heart.

46
00:03:12,350 --> 00:03:13,960
So are the balloons.

47
00:03:14,310 --> 00:03:14,870
Right!

48
00:03:14,910 --> 00:03:15,950
The rose petals should be arranged

49
00:03:15,950 --> 00:03:17,030
in the shape of heart, as well.

50
00:03:17,800 --> 00:03:18,760
That's so cheesy.

51
00:03:19,590 --> 00:03:21,480
[Daily special offers! A special gift for your loved one at 26.66 yuan!]

52
00:03:21,720 --> 00:03:22,870
So people

53
00:03:22,870 --> 00:03:24,190
need these for a proposal.

54
00:03:28,590 --> 00:03:30,870
These are not important.

55
00:03:30,870 --> 00:03:32,079
What's important is

56
00:03:32,110 --> 00:03:34,600
the love behind the surprise.

57
00:03:36,920 --> 00:03:38,470
That's important, of course,

58
00:03:38,470 --> 00:03:39,230
but it's bad that

59
00:03:39,230 --> 00:03:40,510
the surprise turns into a shock.

60
00:03:42,590 --> 00:03:43,760
There's a man

61
00:03:44,110 --> 00:03:45,150
who hid the ring

62
