in a piece of cake for the proposal.

63
00:03:46,520 --> 00:03:47,840
But his girlfriend swallowed the ring

64
00:03:47,840 --> 00:03:49,390
while eating the cake.

65
00:03:49,390 --> 00:03:50,990
If the ring's stuck in her windpipe,

66
00:03:50,990 --> 00:03:52,240
it will be such a tragedy.

67
00:03:54,150 --> 00:03:55,320
Another guy

68
00:03:56,040 --> 00:03:57,040
hid the ring

69
00:03:57,040 --> 00:03:57,720
in his wound.

70
00:03:57,880 --> 00:03:58,560
Then he went to

71
00:03:58,560 --> 00:03:59,630
his girlfriend who's a nurse

72
00:03:59,630 --> 00:04:00,560
to get it out.

73
00:04:00,600 --> 00:04:01,920
Just picture it.

74
00:04:02,480 --> 00:04:04,440
His girlfriend picked the ring out of

75
00:04:04,640 --> 00:04:06,550
the bloody wound

76
